  "body": "With shared informers merged in PR #30825, PV re-sync period is now 3 minutes and more, which is too much for the controller (it was 15 seconds before). E.g. e2e tests for deletion of provisioned volumes take 3-6 minutes longer.\n\nIt could be the reason behind #32492, but it's hard to guess without controller logs.\n\nWe need either shorter sync for this shared informer or revert the PR completely.\n\n@kubernetes/sig-storage \n",
